              <tr>
                <td width="100%" valign="top" align="left">
                  <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="560" class="st-mso-full-width st-mobile-full-width" style="width: 560px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td align="center" valign="top" width="560">
                        <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                          <tr>
                            <td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" class="mob-fz-26 samsung-lineHeight" style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Majrit Tx', Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #000000; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.0313333em; line-height: 36px; padding-top: 20px; width: 100%;">
                              <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px;"><em>Sud&#225;n, dos a&#241;os de terror civil</em></p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                          <tr>
                            <td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" class="bullets-pl20" style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Majrit Tx', Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #000000; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 27px; padding-top: 25px; padding-bottom: 10px; width: 100%;">
                              <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px;">La comunidad internacional no puede seguir ignorando una guerra que ha generado 12 millones de refugiados</p>
                            </td>
