</div>
<div style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:15px; color:#000000; line-height: 25px;text-align:center;" class="name-100">Starship Flight 9 is scheduled to launch no earlier than Tuesday, May 27, at 7:30 p.m. EDT (2330 GMT) from SpaceX's Starbase test site near Boca Chica Beach in South Texas. Like its name suggests, this will be the ninth test flight of the giant SpaceX rocket, but it is the first to attempt to reuse the giant Super Heavy booster, the first stage of Starship.</div>
